### Create Endpoint

```text
POST /api/endpoints
```

Request:

```json
{
  "name": "get_weather",
  "title": "Get Weather",
  "description": "Returns mock weather data",
  "enabled": true,
  "deleteCode": "12345678",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "city",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "City name",
      "required": true
    }
  ],
  "responseCases": [
    {
      "caseName": "Seoul weather",
      "priority": 1,
      "matchJson": {
        "city": "Seoul"
      },
      "responseJson": {
        "city": "Seoul",
        "temperature": 22,
        "condition": "Sunny"
      },
      "isDefault": false,
      "delayMs": 0,
      "errorEnabled": false
    }
  ]
}
```

Response:

```json
{
  "id": "endpoint_uuid",
  "name": "get_weather"
}
```

